{"tid":1330562,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2014到依家2019 我哋改變咗啲乜嘢","createTime":"2019-07-18T15:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T09:10:44.000Z","uid":1330,"like":322,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"8cce67d1903f749afb143064d386df73f2917bc2","tid":1330562,"uid":1330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:22:18.000Z","msg":"5年裏面 我哋口號由提防左膠 變為 不分化不割𥱊<br />\n5年裏面 我哋由見到催淚彈就驚到仆街 變到 識淋熄佢<br />\n5年裏面 我哋由拆大台 到依家家真係冇大台<br />\n5年裏面 我哋屌00後港豬 依家啲00後中學生就走曬出嚟<br />\n5年裏面 hocc由屌衝立會嗰班係鬼 到依家話永遠企係示威者呢邊<br />\n5年裏面 我哋由笑香蕉奶 到笑香蕉糖<br />\n5年裹面 我哋由捱打被動 到主動還拖<br />\n5年裏面 幾多位講過 : 屌 香港冇撚得救㗎喇 嘅義士再次上返前線<br />\n<br />\n當中仲有好多好多改變 <br />\n好多好多嘅血同汗<br />\n好多好多嘅犧牲<br />\n<br />\n攰，係好攰<br />\n灰，係好灰<br />\n但你放心 大把人同你一齊攰 一齊灰<br />\n<br />\n要記住 我哋係喺到做緊歷史<br />\n幾十年後 幾百年後我哋嘅後代(如果仲有) 會點睇我哋 會點讀今日嘅歷史<br />\n就係靠我哋嘅造化同行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7.21</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港島見。</span></span>"},{"pid":"a2fe0ae1ceb55f32cd1ec5a560fc90d52e5329c8","tid":1330562,"uid":6626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:24:08.000Z","msg":"句句心聲<br />\n721見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36d9e2ddde4d343db03d387ab356f2a3754317b","tid":1330562,"uid":1330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2bba857d95597cb1f848fbcca83512ec820651","tid":1330562,"uid":1330,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">二百萬人再一起<br />\n應該不怕旁人不服氣</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face